Function getParent() doesn't listed in the docs. I haven't tried every object ,so I don't know where everywhere is this function missing.

*Example:*
{code:javascript}
var win = Ti.UI.createWindow({
	title: "Hello!"
});

var childView = Ti.UI.createView();

win.add(childView);
